2. Video structure breakdown (how do they hook viewers in first 30 seconds?)
3. Title formulas they use repeatedly
4. Thumbnail style patterns
5. Upload frequency and timing
6. Audience engagement patterns (comment themes, likes/views ratio)
7. Their unique value proposition

